Frank Ellis (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Ellis_(actor) 0 Thomas John Ellis (born 17 November 1978), better known as Tom Ellis, is a British actor from Cardiff, Wales. He is best known for playing Gary Preston in the sitcom Miranda (2009–2015) and Lucifer Morningstar in the American television series Lucifer (2016–).
